QA Automation Framework (API + UI + BDD)

A scalable automation framework using:

Playwright (UI automation)
Requests (API automation)
Pytest + BDD (test orchestration)
Allure Reports (reporting)
YAML-based config system
Makefile for one-command execution

Project Structure:

qa-automation-framework-v1/
│
├── api/
├── ui/
├── tests/
├── utils/
├── config/
├── schemas/
├── reports/
├── conftest.py
├── Makefile
└── .env.example

Setup Instructions:

1. Clone Repository:

git clone <repo-url>
cd qa-automation-framework

2. Create Virtual Environment:

python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

3. Install Dependencies:

make install or pip install -r requirements.txt

4. Install Playwright Browsers:

playwright install

5. Setup Environment File:

cp .env.example .env

Update required values:

ENV=dev
API_KEY=your_key_here

