Framework Features
API Layer:
Retry mechanism
Config-driven base URL
Schema validation
Auth token handling
Logging + Allure integration

UI Layer:
Playwright wrapper (BasePage)
Built-in waits
Screenshot on failure
Reusable assertions

BDD Layer:
Pytest-BDD scenarios
Reusable step definitions
Tag support (@api, @ui)

-------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------

Configuration System:

Environment-based config:

config/environments.yaml

Supports:

dev / staging / prod switching
dynamic env variable injection ${VAR}
API + UI config separation

------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------

Test Execution Flow:

Startup validation runs
Config loaded dynamically
API/UI tests executed
Logs captured
Allure results generated

